WEBVTT

00:01:34.240 --> 00:01:35.800
So about my illness,

00:01:37.080 --> 00:01:39.200
can you keep it a secret for now?

00:01:43.560 --> 00:01:44.880
When the time is right,

00:01:44.880 --> 00:01:46.320
I will tell everyone,

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:47.600
okay?

00:01:51.240 --> 00:01:52.700
I know what you're saying,

00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:55.440
but I don't want to keep it from Wu Wei.

00:01:55.440 --> 00:01:56.759
I think he should know.

00:01:56.759 --> 00:01:57.360
No,

00:01:57.680 --> 00:01:59.320
especially not him.

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:01.960
Right now, the Haoyue-4 mission is just like

00:02:01.960 --> 00:02:03.360
when you guys were in

00:02:03.800 --> 00:02:06.120
the final sprint of the college entrance exam.

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:08.280
All of our combined efforts

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:09.360
are facing a huge test.

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:11.690
I don't want to distract anyone right now.

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:18.720
Let's wait until we get a good grade.

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:20.200
Please.

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:30.920
Okay,

00:02:30.920 --> 00:02:31.720
I promise.

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:37.079
But you must also promise me to get hospitalized soon

00:02:37.079 --> 00:02:38.360
and schedule the surgery.

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:40.040
Okay, I promise.

00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:41.280
I promise you, okay?

00:02:41.600 --> 00:02:42.640
Once the date is set,

00:02:42.640 --> 00:02:43.960
you'll be the first to know.

00:02:43.960 --> 00:02:44.720
And,

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:46.720
you must fully cooperate with the treatment.

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:48.600
What? Are you looking down on me?

00:02:48.880 --> 00:02:50.240
It's just cancer.

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:53.320
I'm ready to fight it for three hundred rounds.

00:02:58.160 --> 00:03:00.280
I still want to see for myself

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:02.880
when we retrieve the lunar soil.

00:03:16.920 --> 00:03:18.480
So about my illness,

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:20.880
can you keep it a secret for now?

00:03:22.320 --> 00:03:23.640
When the time is right,

00:03:23.640 --> 00:03:24.920
I will tell everyone.

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:26.880
Okay?

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:30.880
Ziqi,

00:03:31.320 --> 00:03:32.640
how is your data coming along?

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:33.560
Send it to me.

00:03:47.520 --> 00:03:48.320
Ying Ziqi.

00:03:50.680 --> 00:03:52.340
Ying Ziqi, what are you doing?

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:58.079
I'm talking to you.

00:03:58.079 --> 00:03:59.940
Let's communicate the progress.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:19.930
What does this mean?

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:24.120
What are you trying to prove by sending me this?

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:25.640
Trying to prove your ability?

00:04:25.640 --> 00:04:26.640
Seeing this,

00:04:27.520 --> 00:04:29.780
you should believe in our abilities now.

00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:32.000
We want to share the burden with you.

00:04:32.680 --> 00:04:34.520
I have clearly told you,

00:04:35.520 --> 00:04:36.880
you were seconded here

00:04:36.880 --> 00:04:38.480
to handle software data.

00:04:38.760 --> 00:04:40.880
You don't need to interfere with the plan.

00:04:40.880 --> 00:04:41.610
Understand?

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:45.800
Don't get mad. He didn't mean it.

00:04:48.360 --> 00:04:49.000
Okay.

00:04:51.200 --> 00:04:52.120
You want to prove it,

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:53.200
then prove it.

00:04:53.200 --> 00:04:55.240
Have you checked this plan yourself?

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:57.000
It's full of loopholes and problems.

00:04:57.000 --> 00:04:58.159
Have you checked it?

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:01.920
Speak.

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.600
He definitely wants to do a good job on the task.

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:15.850
You two listen to me.

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:18.000
I know why you two are here.

00:05:18.840 --> 00:05:19.840
But let me tell you both,

00:05:19.840 --> 00:05:20.770
it's not needed.

00:05:21.400 --> 00:05:22.400
You two are here

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:23.880
just to assist with my work.

00:05:23.880 --> 00:05:25.240
Don't think about or do

00:05:25.240 --> 00:05:26.080
things you're not supposed to.

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:27.740
And don't even think about it.

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:30.200
Ying Ziqi.

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:33.240
I know with your reputation as an expert,

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:34.840
you're not happy about assisting me.

00:05:34.840 --> 00:05:36.080
But I gave you a chance before,

00:05:36.080 --> 00:05:37.280
and you didn't take it.

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:38.880
You can't blame anyone else.

00:05:40.600 --> 00:05:42.440
I don't want to say any more nonsense.

00:05:42.440 --> 00:05:44.440
I will emphasize this one last time.

00:05:44.480 --> 00:05:46.880
I will make the plan, and you two do the data.

00:05:47.640 --> 00:05:48.700
Can you cooperate?

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:52.120
Can you?

00:06:22.560 --> 00:06:23.360
Director Cao.

00:06:26.080 --> 00:06:26.720
Old Gu.

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:28.130
I need to talk to you.

00:06:28.640 --> 00:06:29.520
I'm just going to a meeting.

00:06:29.520 --> 00:06:30.400
Let's talk on the way.

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:31.520
No, no, no. I can't wait.

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:32.980
Look at this, look at this.

00:06:44.440 --> 00:06:45.600
When did he find out?

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:47.560
They found out

00:06:47.560 --> 00:06:48.520
during his last physical exam.

00:06:48.520 --> 00:06:50.120
But he never told me.

00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:52.320
The hospital said he wasn't cooperating,

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:54.050
so they contacted us directly.

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:55.240
Anyway,

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:58.800
I took it upon myself to submit his leave application to the center.

00:06:58.800 --> 00:06:59.240
Look at him.

00:06:59.240 --> 00:07:01.480
How can he be so calm?

00:07:01.480 --> 00:07:02.440
At a time like this,

00:07:02.440 --> 00:07:03.800
he didn't say a word.

00:07:04.120 --> 00:07:05.580
I know about this illness.

00:07:05.760 --> 00:07:08.440
When the pain hits, normal people can't bear it.

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:14.040
He's so old,

00:07:14.680 --> 00:07:17.210
and he doesn't have anyone to take care of him.

00:07:24.280 --> 00:07:24.800
Hello.

00:07:27.560 --> 00:07:29.560
I have an emergency to deal with here.

00:07:29.560 --> 00:07:30.920
Postpone the meeting.

00:07:40.840 --> 00:07:42.240
You learned how to knock.

00:07:42.840 --> 00:07:43.640
What's wrong?

00:07:49.800 --> 00:07:50.520
Well...

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:54.480
What's the matter? Why the hesitation?

00:07:58.520 --> 00:07:59.159
Lao Qin.

00:07:59.760 --> 00:08:01.520
We've known each other for so many years.

00:08:01.520 --> 00:08:03.450
Have I ever asked you for anything?

00:08:05.880 --> 00:08:08.240
How else do you plan to ask?

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:09.700
I don't even dare to count.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:10.800
Haven't you asked me enough?

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:11.400
No, no.

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:13.960
Have I ever asked you for anything serious?

00:08:14.600 --> 00:08:16.520
Just say what you want to say.

00:08:17.280 --> 00:08:18.640
I'll agree to it today.

00:08:19.560 --> 00:08:20.280
Come with me.

00:08:20.280 --> 00:08:23.040
Let's go to the hospital for treatment.

00:08:23.960 --> 00:08:26.880
You asked the leaders to transfer me back from Xi'an.

00:08:26.880 --> 00:08:28.280
Isn't it because of this?

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:30.680
No, no, no.

00:08:31.640 --> 00:08:32.840
I won't agree to this.

00:08:42.840 --> 00:08:43.520
Old Gu.

00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:45.080
I won't listen to your nonsense.

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:46.540
I'll give you ten minutes.

00:08:47.720 --> 00:08:48.720
I'm not fooling you.

00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:50.520
You have to hear me out.

00:08:50.520 --> 00:08:51.850
Nine and a half minutes.

00:08:52.360 --> 00:08:55.490
I'm not saying I won't get treatment. What are you doing?

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:57.360
Given the situation,

00:08:57.880 --> 00:08:59.410
I can't avoid this mission.

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:01.480
We need to prioritize

00:09:01.480 --> 00:09:03.010
and look at the big picture.

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:09.050
You love tea, so I'm bringing your teacup.

00:09:09.080 --> 00:09:10.540
Here's your tea canister.

00:09:10.800 --> 00:09:11.440
I'll pack your clothes

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:12.240
and daily necessities,

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:12.960
and once they're packed,

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:14.680
I'll deliver them to the hospital myself.

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:15.080
All right.

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:16.560
What are you doing?

00:09:17.160 --> 00:09:18.600
You're always so bossy.

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:21.320
I feel sorry for my sister-in-law.

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:22.080
Listen to me.

00:09:25.880 --> 00:09:26.960
I'll take full responsibility

00:09:26.960 --> 00:09:29.080
for the lunar landing site and the rover.

00:09:29.080 --> 00:09:29.960
Your task

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:32.690
is to cooperate with the doctors and get treated.

00:09:34.920 --> 00:09:36.240
Fine, how about this?

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:39.040
As soon as the subsystem plan is out,

00:09:39.280 --> 00:09:40.920
I'll go to the hospital right away, okay?

00:09:40.920 --> 00:09:41.760
I promise you.

00:09:47.520 --> 00:09:50.280
The overall plan is only missing these two parts.

00:09:50.280 --> 00:09:51.840
Delaying my hospitalization for two days

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:53.200
isn't a big deal.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:54.360
Right?

00:09:59.520 --> 00:10:00.880
Do you want me to cooperate with you

00:10:00.880 --> 00:10:01.840
and say it loudly here?

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:03.440
No, I don't.

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:04.800
I'll go, okay?

00:10:07.960 --> 00:10:08.760
Fine, I'll go.

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.600
I'll be hospitalized, okay?

00:10:15.720 --> 00:10:17.380
But you have to promise me too.

00:10:18.320 --> 00:10:19.920
We can't let these kids know.

00:10:23.400 --> 00:10:25.440
You are so bossy. You...

00:10:30.920 --> 00:10:32.000
The current problem

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:34.260
is that we are short on time and manpower.

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:35.800
Can we apply to the center

00:10:35.800 --> 00:10:37.000
to transfer Yan back?

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:39.120
It would be good to have an extra hand.

00:10:39.400 --> 00:10:40.920
Transfer Yan back?

00:10:43.720 --> 00:10:45.640
I have an idea.

00:10:45.640 --> 00:10:47.000
I don't think so.

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:49.330
They are really short-handed in Xichang.

00:10:49.560 --> 00:10:50.440
How about this?

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:52.040
We divide the work.

00:10:52.040 --> 00:10:54.370
You take charge of the Apollo basin, okay?

00:10:55.160 --> 00:10:56.290
What about the rest?

00:10:57.160 --> 00:10:59.160
I'll take charge of Von Kármán and Schrödinger.

00:10:59.160 --> 00:11:01.040
I've already done some work on them anyway.

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:03.840
I believe as long as we work together,

00:11:03.840 --> 00:11:05.400
we can definitely catch the launch window.

00:11:05.400 --> 00:11:06.400
Von Kármán?

00:11:08.560 --> 00:11:10.560
That's a bit of an unpopular choice.

00:11:12.040 --> 00:11:13.160
The Von Kármán crater,

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:14.640
compared to other sites,

00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:15.680
has lower scientific value,

00:11:15.680 --> 00:11:17.440
and the data is not clear enough.

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:18.720
It's easily overlooked.

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:21.320
But considering the Haoyue-4 mission,

00:11:21.320 --> 00:11:23.360
providing supplies for the Rabbit on the far side of the moon,

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:25.320
and the controllable altitude

00:11:25.320 --> 00:11:26.640
and time differences

00:11:26.640 --> 00:11:28.240
during the landing process,

00:11:28.280 --> 00:11:29.640
the basin advantage of Von Kármán

00:11:29.640 --> 00:11:30.700
becomes apparent.

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:32.920
Okay.

00:11:33.400 --> 00:11:34.360
We can't worry too much about it.

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:36.080
Let's start the screening again.

00:11:36.080 --> 00:11:36.720
Um,

00:11:37.480 --> 00:11:39.360
Mr. Jiang, Jiajia,

00:11:39.640 --> 00:11:41.120
I have an idea.

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:44.000
I want to apply for a landing site plan alone.

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:45.730
Caibao and I can do it together.

00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:49.520
What's going on, Nan?

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:52.280
We will definitely finish the plan by ourselves.

00:11:52.280 --> 00:11:54.940
I promise not to slow down everyone's progress.

00:11:59.880 --> 00:12:00.440
Okay.

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:02.240
Then you two will be responsible for Schrödinger.

00:12:02.240 --> 00:12:02.840
All right.

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:05.840
Then if anyone has any problems, feel free to communicate at any time.

00:12:05.840 --> 00:12:06.570
Understood.

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:09.320
Let's get to work.

00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:13.740
What's the situation?

00:12:21.240 --> 00:12:22.880
What are you doing?

00:12:23.280 --> 00:12:24.520
If I hitch you to a millstone,

00:12:24.520 --> 00:12:26.520
we'll be provided for in our old age.

00:12:27.120 --> 00:12:28.960
Fine, you can call me a donkey.

00:12:29.160 --> 00:12:31.320
I don't care what you call me.

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:40.560
Listen to me.

00:12:40.920 --> 00:12:41.920
Here's the thing.

00:12:43.160 --> 00:12:45.800
The hospital leaders talked to me.

00:12:46.040 --> 00:12:47.000
They said for your condition,

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:49.840
the director will perform the surgery himself.

00:12:51.240 --> 00:12:52.600
It might be scheduled soon,

00:12:52.600 --> 00:12:53.960
so be prepared.

00:12:57.360 --> 00:12:59.020
I'm asking you. Are you ready?

00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:00.240
Did you hear me?

00:13:01.360 --> 00:13:02.200
I heard you.

00:13:05.560 --> 00:13:07.160
Stop reading. Stop reading.

00:13:07.840 --> 00:13:09.480
I'm just looking at a few documents.

00:13:09.480 --> 00:13:10.720
I'm not working.

00:13:11.080 --> 00:13:12.540
Alright, no more reading.

00:13:13.880 --> 00:13:16.240
Look at Xiao Chu, she's undecided.

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:18.320
So Xu Xu's situation can't be settled either.

00:13:18.320 --> 00:13:20.400
I'm just anxious.

00:13:20.400 --> 00:13:21.840
What are you anxious about? Give it to me.

00:13:21.840 --> 00:13:22.720
Can we negotiate?

00:13:22.720 --> 00:13:24.120
I'm telling you, this is non-negotiable.

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:25.520
How about I just work for one hour a day?

00:13:25.520 --> 00:13:26.360
Is that okay?

00:13:26.360 --> 00:13:26.800
No.

00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:27.720
Not even one.

00:13:27.720 --> 00:13:28.320
Hands off.

00:13:29.040 --> 00:13:30.360
Not even one hour?

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:33.200
Making me lie here every day,

00:13:33.200 --> 00:13:34.680
isn't it a waste of national resources?

00:13:34.680 --> 00:13:36.200
What is this?

00:13:36.200 --> 00:13:37.320
In the end,

00:13:37.760 --> 00:13:39.760
you even found someone to manage me.

00:13:39.840 --> 00:13:40.520
You are good.

00:13:40.520 --> 00:13:43.120
Just wait. One day I'll tell you

00:13:44.040 --> 00:13:45.320
my computer password

00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:46.780
and my bank card password.

00:13:46.920 --> 00:13:47.800
When I die,

00:13:47.800 --> 00:13:49.120
take my inheritance,

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:50.200
and you have to

00:13:50.200 --> 00:13:52.360
let those guys work with you.

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:53.960
But,

00:13:53.960 --> 00:13:56.240
you must use the fund for its intended purpose.

00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:58.480
That's bullshit. You're just...

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:01.760
Let me tell you.

00:14:03.160 --> 00:14:04.120
We agreed back then,

00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:05.880
we would do this

00:14:06.080 --> 00:14:07.280
Raoluohui together.

00:14:08.280 --> 00:14:10.120
No one is allowed to be a deserter, right?

00:14:10.120 --> 00:14:11.520
When we put our fingerprints on it,

00:14:11.520 --> 00:14:12.920
we made a promise to each other.

00:14:12.920 --> 00:14:13.920
Let me tell you.

00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:15.160
I can keep an eye

00:14:15.160 --> 00:14:17.040
on both sides of the work for you now.

00:14:17.040 --> 00:14:17.560
Your task

00:14:17.560 --> 00:14:19.480
is to recuperate well here.

00:14:19.480 --> 00:14:20.600
When you recover,

00:14:20.600 --> 00:14:22.400
I'll leave all this to you,

00:14:22.400 --> 00:14:23.760
and then I'll take a vacation, okay?

00:14:23.760 --> 00:14:25.000
I'll work you to death, you old thing.

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:26.200
Huang Shiren.

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:27.840
So bossy.

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:32.880
You just know how to bully a poor old woman like me.

00:14:32.880 --> 00:14:33.480
Don't you?

00:14:34.240 --> 00:14:36.640
Just be good.

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:38.540
Focus on recovering here.

00:14:41.200 --> 00:14:41.760
I'm leaving.

00:14:41.760 --> 00:14:42.760
Recover well, hear me?

00:14:42.760 --> 00:14:44.480
You annoy me.

00:15:02.960 --> 00:15:05.240
The mantis stalks the cicada,

00:15:07.720 --> 00:15:08.980
unaware of the oriole.

00:15:09.880 --> 00:15:11.360
Why are you back again?

00:15:11.640 --> 00:15:12.680
Let me tell you.

00:15:12.920 --> 00:15:14.160
Don't play these childish games with me.

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:15.520
You only have three things to do in the hospital.

00:15:15.520 --> 00:15:17.040
First, listen to the doctor.

00:15:17.040 --> 00:15:18.080
Second, listen to the nurses.

00:15:18.080 --> 00:15:19.720
Third, listen to me.

00:15:19.800 --> 00:15:20.720
Listen. Get some rest.

00:15:20.720 --> 00:15:22.780
I'll listen to you. Drink some water.

00:15:23.840 --> 00:15:24.400
No.

00:15:26.200 --> 00:15:28.120
Then can you listen to me?

00:15:28.120 --> 00:15:30.240
Just don't tell them about that.

00:15:30.240 --> 00:15:31.200
Don't forget.

00:15:41.160 --> 00:15:43.840
Aerospace flight control...

00:15:50.440 --> 00:15:52.320
What's up with Mr. Gu?

00:15:52.720 --> 00:15:54.200
He looks so stressed.

00:15:54.680 --> 00:15:56.140
Mr. Qin isn't here either.

00:15:56.280 --> 00:15:57.600
It's so intimidating.

00:16:01.280 --> 00:16:01.840
Listen.

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:03.680
Jiajia, Mengyao.

00:16:03.680 --> 00:16:04.520
You need to figure out

00:16:04.520 --> 00:16:06.560
the optimal plan for me as soon as possible.

00:16:06.560 --> 00:16:07.200
Yes, yes.

00:16:07.400 --> 00:16:08.800
As for the inner field...

00:16:10.400 --> 00:16:11.440
Wu Wei, Ziqi.

00:16:11.880 --> 00:16:13.040
You have three days

00:16:13.040 --> 00:16:14.200
to coordinate with Xu Xu.

00:16:14.200 --> 00:16:16.600
Make sure to finish the subsystem software plan

00:16:16.600 --> 00:16:18.760
and start the obstacle avoidance test ASAP.

00:16:18.760 --> 00:16:19.490
Understood.

00:16:20.440 --> 00:16:21.600
Mr. Qin.

00:16:22.040 --> 00:16:23.720
During this closed-door meeting,

00:16:23.720 --> 00:16:25.000
I will be responsible for coordinating

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:27.280
the work arrangements of both your teams.

00:16:27.280 --> 00:16:29.120
We've fallen too far behind schedule.

00:16:29.120 --> 00:16:30.050
We must hurry up.

00:16:30.720 --> 00:16:32.280
I heard that a couple of days ago,

00:16:32.280 --> 00:16:34.040
at the international academic symposium,

00:16:34.040 --> 00:16:35.900
our mission was being discussed.

00:16:36.360 --> 00:16:37.490
What does this mean?

00:16:42.040 --> 00:16:43.920
It means the eyes of the whole world

00:16:43.920 --> 00:16:45.200
are on us.

00:16:46.920 --> 00:16:48.880
Whether we can go to the far side of the moon

00:16:48.880 --> 00:16:50.340
depends on everyone here.

00:16:54.240 --> 00:16:55.040
Let's do this.

00:17:08.000 --> 00:17:09.520
What's wrong?

00:17:09.520 --> 00:17:10.780
You don't look so good.

00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:12.359
Nothing.

00:17:12.359 --> 00:17:14.220
I might just be a bit tired lately.

00:17:14.760 --> 00:17:15.760
Let's do our best.

00:17:16.839 --> 00:17:19.170
You need to hurry up with the landing plan.

00:17:20.520 --> 00:17:21.650
I'll get going then.

00:17:59.120 --> 00:18:00.320
Can you stop spinning?

00:18:00.320 --> 00:18:01.600
It's making me dizzy.

00:18:03.880 --> 00:18:05.340
Let's check our progress.

00:18:08.320 --> 00:18:10.360
I should be done by tomorrow morning.

00:18:10.360 --> 00:18:12.160
What about you? How much is left?

00:18:13.560 --> 00:18:14.840
I'm almost done.

00:18:15.360 --> 00:18:16.800
What do you mean almost?

00:18:16.800 --> 00:18:18.200
Can you be more specific?

00:18:25.480 --> 00:18:27.280
Why have you only done so little?

00:18:28.720 --> 00:18:30.880
What have you been doing these past two days?

00:18:30.880 --> 00:18:32.080
I've been here all the time.

00:18:32.080 --> 00:18:33.740
Haven't you seen me every day?

00:18:33.840 --> 00:18:34.480
Besides.

00:18:34.480 --> 00:18:36.810
Calculation really isn't my strong suit.

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:37.640
Nan.

00:18:37.840 --> 00:18:40.240
How about we go back and get a good sleep today,

00:18:40.240 --> 00:18:42.040
and continue tomorrow morning?

00:18:42.480 --> 00:18:44.740
Don't you know how tight the schedule is?

00:18:45.960 --> 00:18:46.840
I know, I know.

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:48.620
I'll do it properly right now.

00:18:49.840 --> 00:18:51.200
Can you stop saying

00:18:51.200 --> 00:18:53.200
you know every time I criticize you?

00:18:53.520 --> 00:18:55.680
Can you show some real action?

00:18:55.920 --> 00:18:57.240
Weren't you the one who made a promise to Jia

00:18:57.240 --> 00:18:58.240
earlier today?

00:18:58.960 --> 00:19:01.760
Did you swallow those words along with your water?

00:19:25.520 --> 00:19:26.160
Nan.

00:19:26.600 --> 00:19:27.730
I've made up my mind.

00:19:27.760 --> 00:19:28.920
I will stay up late today

00:19:28.920 --> 00:19:30.320
and calculate properly.

00:19:30.320 --> 00:19:31.680
I'm going to buy a coffee.

00:19:31.680 --> 00:19:32.610
Do you want some?

00:19:34.920 --> 00:19:37.320
A China Aerospace iced Americano, thanks.

00:19:57.840 --> 00:19:59.080
Take my big...

00:20:12.880 --> 00:20:13.940
[China Aerospace]

00:20:18.160 --> 00:20:19.820
Where did you go to buy coffee?

00:20:21.880 --> 00:20:23.360
Got the first win.

00:20:27.680 --> 00:20:29.760
Share it with Dafu.

00:20:42.320 --> 00:20:43.160
My God.

00:20:43.400 --> 00:20:44.520
It's over.

00:21:15.600 --> 00:21:16.200
Passed.

00:21:17.600 --> 00:21:18.530
Finally passed.

00:21:21.280 --> 00:21:24.410
The data in this version is much better than the last one.

00:21:24.840 --> 00:21:28.600
Now we can start the physical vehicle testing, right?

00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:37.640
Not yet.

00:21:38.680 --> 00:21:40.280
This plan is still not ideal.

00:21:40.320 --> 00:21:41.880
It's not the perfect solution.

00:21:41.880 --> 00:21:42.520
Reset.

00:21:43.120 --> 00:21:43.920
Do it again.

00:21:45.360 --> 00:21:45.960
Why?

00:21:48.040 --> 00:21:49.720
The comprehensive electronic subsystem feedback

00:21:49.720 --> 00:21:50.800
is still not good enough.

00:21:50.800 --> 00:21:51.760
This result,

00:21:52.120 --> 00:21:54.080
you can accept it, but I can't.

00:21:54.400 --> 00:21:56.280
Even if the deviation is only one in ten thousand,

00:21:56.280 --> 00:21:58.600
it's a devastating blow on the far side of the moon.

00:21:58.600 --> 00:22:00.160
Problems that occurred in the past

00:22:00.160 --> 00:22:01.560
must never happen again.

00:22:02.120 --> 00:22:03.380
Just understand this.

00:22:10.760 --> 00:22:12.400
Deal with your useless emotions yourself.

00:22:12.400 --> 00:22:13.440
This is a workplace.

00:22:13.440 --> 00:22:15.100
Please be more professional.

00:22:15.160 --> 00:22:18.120
I don't know if I'm capable or professional.

00:22:18.720 --> 00:22:20.760
You are the senior. You know best.

00:22:20.760 --> 00:22:22.120
Come on, senior, teach me.

00:22:22.120 --> 00:22:23.040
In just these two days,

00:22:23.040 --> 00:22:24.440
how do I change the proposal to your liking?

00:22:24.440 --> 00:22:25.600
If you don't want to do it, just say so.

00:22:25.600 --> 00:22:26.560
Stop being so sarcastic

00:22:26.560 --> 00:22:27.920
and wasting each other's time.

00:22:27.920 --> 00:22:29.240
I'm wasting time?

00:22:29.520 --> 00:22:30.600
Which piece of data we prepared

00:22:30.600 --> 00:22:31.600
isn't what you asked for?

00:22:31.600 --> 00:22:33.120
You have a set of standards in your mind,

00:22:33.120 --> 00:22:34.520
but you don't communicate with us.

00:22:34.520 --> 00:22:36.000
Right, you're the boss.

00:22:36.000 --> 00:22:38.400
We can wait, but can the window period wait?

00:22:41.080 --> 00:22:42.600
Today's proposal can go back to zero.

00:22:42.600 --> 00:22:43.720
But you must come up with

00:22:43.720 --> 00:22:44.920
a passing standard.

00:22:45.400 --> 00:22:46.480
Aren't we

00:22:50.760 --> 00:22:51.890
communicating now?

00:22:52.800 --> 00:22:54.000
Xu Xu is also trying to ensure

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:55.360
the task is foolproof.

00:22:55.840 --> 00:22:57.040
We said we'd cooperate,

00:22:57.040 --> 00:22:58.500
so let's trust each other.

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:00.600
You're speaking for him?

00:23:00.600 --> 00:23:02.800
Don't say that. It's all for the Rabbit.

00:23:03.080 --> 00:23:05.210
Don't be emotional. Let's work first.

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:07.400
Can't I be emotional?

00:23:08.120 --> 00:23:09.560
Only three people are doing the task,

00:23:09.560 --> 00:23:11.200
all revolving around him.

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:12.880
When you need data urgently, we stay up late to work overtime.

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:14.400
Have I ever said no?

00:23:14.400 --> 00:23:15.840
If you are really worried about the task failing,

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:17.960
we should work hard on the same plan.

00:23:17.960 --> 00:23:19.440
But you overturn it as you please.

00:23:19.440 --> 00:23:20.300
Let me tell you.

00:23:20.440 --> 00:23:22.000
What's useless is not my emotions.

00:23:22.000 --> 00:23:22.720
It's you.

00:23:25.960 --> 00:23:27.120
Leave quickly if you want to.

00:23:27.120 --> 00:23:28.280
If not, work hard.

00:23:46.040 --> 00:23:47.370
Sister Nan. Sister Nan.

00:23:47.560 --> 00:23:48.880
Drink some coffee, Sister Nan.

00:23:48.880 --> 00:23:49.940
Drink it yourself.

00:23:50.000 --> 00:23:51.080
Don't, don't, don't. Don't be mad.

00:23:51.080 --> 00:23:52.080
I know I was wrong.

00:23:52.600 --> 00:23:53.600
You are not wrong.

00:23:53.960 --> 00:23:54.920
If you really don't want to do it,

00:23:54.920 --> 00:23:56.160
you can actually tell me directly.

00:23:56.160 --> 00:23:57.160
No need to hide it from me.

00:23:57.160 --> 00:23:58.820
Don't you like playing games?

00:23:59.080 --> 00:24:00.920
You can also play professionally.

00:24:00.920 --> 00:24:02.880
It's also winning glory for the country.

00:24:02.880 --> 00:24:03.480
Oh, right.

00:24:03.680 --> 00:24:05.340
You can also go play the drums.

00:24:05.560 --> 00:24:06.560
Beating a retreat.

00:24:06.560 --> 00:24:07.800
You must be the best in the world.

00:24:07.800 --> 00:24:08.760
It's wrong for me to lie to you.

00:24:08.760 --> 00:24:09.440
But during this time,

00:24:09.440 --> 00:24:11.480
I've been struggling with that landing point every day.

00:24:11.480 --> 00:24:13.160
Even computers need rest.

00:24:13.160 --> 00:24:14.160
Sleepless for so many days,

00:24:14.160 --> 00:24:15.640
I really can't hold on anymore.

00:24:15.640 --> 00:24:16.560
I know playing games is wrong.

00:24:16.560 --> 00:24:17.360
And I'm anxious when I play.

00:24:17.360 --> 00:24:19.160
I can't play well either, but...

00:24:19.240 --> 00:24:21.500
I'm really not ready to be the main force.

00:24:22.160 --> 00:24:22.920
I'm sorry.

00:24:25.840 --> 00:24:27.700
You don't need to apologize to me.

00:24:29.480 --> 00:24:31.410
You should apologize to yourself.

00:24:32.160 --> 00:24:32.720
You should apologize to

00:24:32.720 --> 00:24:34.840
this job you stick to.

00:24:36.440 --> 00:24:38.100
If you don't want to work hard,

00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:40.370
you don't need to make so many excuses.

00:24:41.200 --> 00:24:43.600
Who here doesn't want to rest?

00:24:43.600 --> 00:24:45.120
But who isn't holding on?

00:24:45.680 --> 00:24:46.320
Tired?

00:24:46.600 --> 00:24:47.600
Who isn't tired?

00:24:48.200 --> 00:24:49.280
I admit whatever you say.

00:24:49.280 --> 00:24:50.720
When have I not worked hard?

00:24:50.720 --> 00:24:52.280
I only sleep for three hours every day.

00:24:52.280 --> 00:24:53.600
I calculated so much data.

00:24:53.600 --> 00:24:54.840
My eyes are getting blurry now.

00:24:54.840 --> 00:24:56.770
I see double images of everything.

00:25:02.960 --> 00:25:03.820
You want to win.

00:25:04.120 --> 00:25:05.480
I want to win too.

00:25:07.400 --> 00:25:10.000
I really just went out for a breath of fresh air.

00:25:11.160 --> 00:25:12.560
Can I go back and do it now?

00:25:16.560 --> 00:25:17.120
Enough.

00:25:18.520 --> 00:25:19.600
You keep playing.

00:25:26.360 --> 00:25:28.420
The window period has been advanced.

00:25:28.560 --> 00:25:31.440
All of us are running forward under pressure.

00:25:32.760 --> 00:25:35.280
Why are you the only one retreating?

00:25:39.880 --> 00:25:40.640
Do you think this place

00:25:40.640 --> 00:25:43.100
is still the ivory tower of your school days?

00:25:44.120 --> 00:25:45.560
Do you think you can still be carefree,

00:25:45.560 --> 00:25:46.520
like a child,

00:25:46.520 --> 00:25:47.960
hiding behind everyone?

00:25:50.280 --> 00:25:51.120
Cai Boao.

00:25:54.840 --> 00:25:56.920
Even people in our hometown know

00:25:57.240 --> 00:25:58.760
Haoyue 4 is about to be completed.

00:25:58.760 --> 00:26:00.890
They are all waiting for our good news.

00:26:01.800 --> 00:26:03.130
Can you grow up quickly?

00:26:03.480 --> 00:26:04.840
Can you be more mature?

00:26:04.840 --> 00:26:05.800
Can you be worthy of

00:26:05.800 --> 00:26:07.400
the clothes you are wearing?

00:26:10.600 --> 00:26:11.760
I'm begging you.

00:26:46.560 --> 00:26:47.400
Where are you?

00:26:48.160 --> 00:26:49.290
I want to talk to you.

00:26:51.880 --> 00:26:54.600
I'm at the space experience center right now.

00:26:54.640 --> 00:26:55.880
Come find me.

00:27:21.760 --> 00:27:23.280
It's almost closed and everyone is off work.

00:27:23.280 --> 00:27:24.440
What if you fall?

00:27:25.880 --> 00:27:28.610
I'm just playing for a bit to relieve some stress.

00:27:29.560 --> 00:27:31.490
Why didn't you ask me to come along?

00:27:31.920 --> 00:27:33.560
The mission is a bit stressful.

00:27:33.560 --> 00:27:34.640
I'm not in a good mood,

00:27:34.640 --> 00:27:36.300
and I'm kind of breaking down.

00:27:38.360 --> 00:27:39.220
What about you?

00:27:39.720 --> 00:27:41.280
You came to find me late at night.

00:27:41.280 --> 00:27:43.210
It can't be just to say this, right?

00:27:45.280 --> 00:27:46.810
Your plan isn't going well.

00:27:47.960 --> 00:27:50.090
Come down first. Let's talk down here.

00:27:53.560 --> 00:27:54.280
All right.

00:28:01.160 --> 00:28:02.680
Actually, I'm pretty much like you.

00:28:02.680 --> 00:28:04.240
There's been a lot of pressure from missions lately.

00:28:04.240 --> 00:28:06.200
And a lot has happened.

00:28:06.840 --> 00:28:07.600
Yeah.

00:28:08.760 --> 00:28:10.200
Come to think of it,

00:28:10.560 --> 00:28:12.560
we've only been here for over a year.

00:28:13.000 --> 00:28:15.200
We thought we had experienced everything.

00:28:15.200 --> 00:28:16.560
But now we realize

00:28:16.960 --> 00:28:18.620
we haven't seen anything yet.

00:28:20.520 --> 00:28:24.180
Isn't our line of work about overcoming one hurdle after another?

00:28:24.440 --> 00:28:25.880
Our current mission

00:28:26.280 --> 00:28:28.240
and the many problems in the future

00:28:28.840 --> 00:28:30.600
are all new unknowns.

00:28:32.640 --> 00:28:34.000
Just now, while I was experiencing it,

00:28:34.000 --> 00:28:34.960
I was thinking.

00:28:35.640 --> 00:28:37.100
Isn't the current mission

00:28:37.680 --> 00:28:39.760
exactly what I wanted to do?

00:28:40.800 --> 00:28:42.060
I'm having a hard time.

00:28:42.320 --> 00:28:44.920
But isn't everyone else having a hard time too?

00:28:48.760 --> 00:28:50.600
Why mix in emotions

00:28:50.760 --> 00:28:52.480
and unnecessary obstacles?

00:28:53.760 --> 00:28:55.880
Complaining comes from thinking.

00:28:56.880 --> 00:28:58.480
Then just don't think about it.

00:28:58.480 --> 00:29:00.120
Just do it and be done with it.

00:29:00.760 --> 00:29:01.720
Look at Wu Wei.

00:29:02.080 --> 00:29:03.760
Isn't his reckless spirit

00:29:03.760 --> 00:29:05.400
quite intoxicating?

00:29:08.520 --> 00:29:09.360
You are right.

00:29:11.400 --> 00:29:12.520
Actually, sometimes I don't know

00:29:12.520 --> 00:29:14.120
if I'm doing the right thing.

00:29:16.400 --> 00:29:18.660
I shouldn't have kept it from my brother.

00:29:19.600 --> 00:29:20.720
But I still did.

00:29:23.920 --> 00:29:26.680
Between good friends and good brothers,

00:29:26.680 --> 00:29:28.940
there's no need to have so many concerns.

00:29:30.640 --> 00:29:31.400
No one

00:29:31.400 --> 00:29:33.530
can truly understand another person.

00:29:34.040 --> 00:29:35.760
Even for the best of brothers,

00:29:36.360 --> 00:29:38.320
actually, between the two of you,

00:29:38.800 --> 00:29:40.360
since you care about him so much,

00:29:40.360 --> 00:29:42.320
he must care about you too.

00:29:42.720 --> 00:29:43.600
Right?

00:29:44.120 --> 00:29:45.280
You have to trust him.

00:29:45.280 --> 00:29:47.000
Believe that your bond

00:29:47.000 --> 00:29:48.960
won't be easily broken.

00:29:50.760 --> 00:29:52.680
And I believe

00:29:52.680 --> 00:29:53.560
that you already have

00:29:53.560 --> 00:29:55.320
the right answer in your heart.

00:29:55.760 --> 00:29:57.490
Then just trust your own choice

00:29:57.640 --> 00:29:58.680
and go do it.

00:30:09.480 --> 00:30:10.280
Thank you.

00:30:10.960 --> 00:30:11.680
You too.

00:30:12.120 --> 00:30:13.450
Relax and do your tasks.

00:30:15.840 --> 00:30:16.680
Who is inside?

00:30:17.280 --> 00:30:18.560
Didn't you know it's closed?

00:30:18.560 --> 00:30:19.620
Come out. Let's go.

00:31:16.200 --> 00:31:17.260
What are you doing?

00:31:17.280 --> 00:31:18.210
Don't bother me.

00:31:22.200 --> 00:31:22.800
Chao.

00:31:28.400 --> 00:31:29.260
Are you crying?

00:31:30.440 --> 00:31:31.100
No, I'm not.

00:31:34.000 --> 00:31:35.000
It's all wet.

00:31:36.160 --> 00:31:37.290
I really didn't cry.

00:31:37.400 --> 00:31:39.600
It's okay to cry. It's not embarrassing.

00:31:39.600 --> 00:31:40.730
Did you get scolded?

00:31:45.800 --> 00:31:46.860
About the mission?

00:31:51.520 --> 00:31:52.200
Chao.

00:31:53.720 --> 00:31:54.600
Do you think it's because

00:31:54.600 --> 00:31:56.200
I came from the gifted class,

00:31:57.360 --> 00:31:59.560
I don't have as much experience as them,

00:31:59.720 --> 00:32:02.180
I'm not mature enough in handling problems,

00:32:02.680 --> 00:32:05.410
and that's why I'm always holding everyone back?

00:32:08.480 --> 00:32:10.800
What's wrong with coming from the gifted class?

00:32:10.800 --> 00:32:13.130
Don't blame your own problems on your age.

00:32:13.160 --> 00:32:14.960
I came from the gifted class too.

00:32:18.560 --> 00:32:19.280
Chao.

00:32:20.920 --> 00:32:21.960
I always thought...

00:32:21.960 --> 00:32:22.800
Thought what?

00:32:23.800 --> 00:32:25.660
I just look a bit mature for my age.

00:32:25.880 --> 00:32:27.680
I'm not that much older than you.

00:32:34.880 --> 00:32:37.000
I remember when I first started school.

00:32:37.000 --> 00:32:38.530
I had an early growth spurt,

00:32:38.720 --> 00:32:40.580
so I was as skinny as a bean sprout.

00:32:40.720 --> 00:32:41.920
Openly and secretly,

00:32:42.040 --> 00:32:43.100
I got bullied a lot.

00:32:44.520 --> 00:32:45.840
Most of my classmates

00:32:46.320 --> 00:32:48.040
were immature boys.

00:32:48.440 --> 00:32:49.480
Their methods

00:32:49.480 --> 00:32:50.880
weren't exactly decent.

00:32:53.440 --> 00:32:54.300
As time went by,

00:32:54.880 --> 00:32:57.000
I actually became what they wanted me to be,

00:32:57.000 --> 00:32:58.760
withdrawn and insecure.

00:33:01.200 --> 00:33:03.240
Later, I joined flight control.

00:33:05.560 --> 00:33:07.600
The mockery only got worse.

00:33:08.000 --> 00:33:09.260
They all laughed at me,

00:33:09.600 --> 00:33:11.960
saying I was just a nerd.

00:33:12.480 --> 00:33:13.540
After graduation,

00:33:13.640 --> 00:33:14.560
I took a poorly paid,

00:33:14.560 --> 00:33:16.000
hard and tiring job.

00:33:16.480 --> 00:33:17.680
I was such a fool.

00:33:18.040 --> 00:33:19.280
You're not a fool.

00:33:20.000 --> 00:33:21.600
I think you are amazing, bro.

00:33:23.200 --> 00:33:23.840
Really.

00:33:24.520 --> 00:33:26.320
I don't care what they think.

00:33:28.280 --> 00:33:29.810
I chose to work in aerospace

00:33:30.280 --> 00:33:32.240
just to achieve my small step,

00:33:32.240 --> 00:33:33.400
one giant leap for mankind,

00:33:33.400 --> 00:33:35.130
this kind of magnificent life.

00:33:37.320 --> 00:33:37.880
Chao.

00:33:39.760 --> 00:33:41.560
Have you learned anything?

00:33:44.000 --> 00:33:45.200
Learned anything?

00:33:46.800 --> 00:33:49.060
We've been in flight control for so long,

00:33:49.280 --> 00:33:52.140
what we experience most are setbacks and failures.

00:33:53.280 --> 00:33:55.040
But if we want to do a good job in aerospace,

00:33:55.040 --> 00:33:56.900
we have to withstand the pressure

00:33:57.000 --> 00:33:58.600
and bear the responsibility.

00:33:58.600 --> 00:33:59.800
To hone ourselves in silence,

00:33:59.800 --> 00:34:00.930
to fight in silence,

00:34:00.960 --> 00:34:02.120
to grow in silence.

00:34:04.840 --> 00:34:05.520
Got it?

00:34:07.480 --> 00:34:08.719
I think so.

00:34:09.960 --> 00:34:10.520
Chao.

00:34:11.159 --> 00:34:12.560
I want to be stronger too.

00:34:12.679 --> 00:34:14.440
Can you share some experience with me?

00:34:14.440 --> 00:34:15.570
Want to be stronger?

00:34:19.080 --> 00:34:20.520
Secret recipe for getting stronger.

00:34:20.520 --> 00:34:21.120
Take a sip.

00:34:23.920 --> 00:34:24.560
I drank it.

00:34:29.040 --> 00:34:30.600
What is this? It's so spicy.

00:34:31.960 --> 00:34:33.199
Liquor and garlic.

00:34:33.199 --> 00:34:34.320
Does this work?

00:34:34.520 --> 00:34:35.400
Definitely.

00:34:35.960 --> 00:34:37.290
Can it make me stronger?

00:34:40.480 --> 00:34:42.210
Save some for me. Drink slowly.

00:34:47.960 --> 00:34:48.820
Let me tell you.

00:34:49.480 --> 00:34:51.080
There used to be a scientist.

00:34:51.520 --> 00:34:52.880
He saw how smart I was

00:34:52.880 --> 00:34:54.880
and that I was a good fit for the aerospace industry.

00:34:54.880 --> 00:34:56.400
For the sake of our country's aerospace cause,

00:34:56.400 --> 00:34:57.330
he used a machine

00:34:57.920 --> 00:34:59.780
to make me muscular in an instant.

00:34:59.960 --> 00:35:00.640
Chao,

00:35:01.400 --> 00:35:03.480
you've got a superhero's script.

00:35:05.520 --> 00:35:07.080
Life is not a movie.

00:35:07.640 --> 00:35:08.880
There won't always be someone

00:35:08.880 --> 00:35:10.880
coming to help you at a critical moment.

00:35:10.880 --> 00:35:13.210
Likewise, no one can predict the outcome.

00:35:13.440 --> 00:35:14.280
People,

00:35:14.280 --> 00:35:15.360
if they don't push themselves,

00:35:15.360 --> 00:35:16.720
will never change.

00:35:18.720 --> 00:35:19.640
To get fit,

00:35:20.240 --> 00:35:21.640
I spent time studying it.

00:35:22.280 --> 00:35:24.960
I planned step by step, starting with my diet,

00:35:25.440 --> 00:35:26.840
and slowly made changes.

00:35:28.000 --> 00:35:28.880
Of course,

00:35:28.880 --> 00:35:30.680
sometimes I also want to be lazy,

00:35:31.320 --> 00:35:32.840
but looking back at my past self,

00:35:32.840 --> 00:35:34.520
I definitely don't want to go back.

00:35:34.520 --> 00:35:36.450
I gritted my teeth and persevered.

00:35:37.120 --> 00:35:38.980
Slowly, I found myself changing.

00:35:40.280 --> 00:35:42.540
I became stronger and more disciplined.

00:35:44.000 --> 00:35:45.600
And I started going bald too.

00:35:50.960 --> 00:35:52.520
Working out

00:35:52.520 --> 00:35:53.980
is just like doing a quest.

00:35:54.080 --> 00:35:56.440
Make a plan, find the flaws, adjust the strategy.

00:35:56.440 --> 00:35:58.160
Achieve small goals one by one,

00:35:58.160 --> 00:36:00.360
and finally achieve the ultimate goal.

00:36:01.920 --> 00:36:02.520
Chao.

00:36:04.760 --> 00:36:05.880
Then let me

00:36:06.600 --> 00:36:08.000
tell you my story too.

00:36:08.760 --> 00:36:09.280
Okay.

00:36:09.280 --> 00:36:10.810
Let's go and talk on the way.

00:36:11.480 --> 00:36:12.520
Let's go.

00:36:31.280 --> 00:36:32.740
Wu Wei, what are you doing?

00:36:35.120 --> 00:36:36.720
I have something to tell you.

00:36:36.880 --> 00:36:37.740
If you are free,

00:36:38.640 --> 00:36:40.100
let's go get some skewers.

00:36:40.520 --> 00:36:42.180
I'll wait for you downstairs.

00:36:51.040 --> 00:36:51.640
Mr. Gu.

00:36:52.440 --> 00:36:53.000
Ziqi.

00:36:53.840 --> 00:36:55.040
The hospital called.

00:36:55.680 --> 00:36:57.680
Old Qin's surgery time has changed.

00:36:58.320 --> 00:36:59.120
It's moved up.

00:37:00.280 --> 00:37:01.210
Is it confirmed?

00:37:02.440 --> 00:37:04.360
It's confirmed. It's tonight.

00:37:05.080 --> 00:37:06.940
I'll wait for you at the main gate.

00:37:08.400 --> 00:37:10.000
Okay, I'm heading there now.

00:37:17.160 --> 00:37:18.620
Wu Wei, what are you doing?

00:37:20.000 --> 00:37:21.600
I have something to tell you.

00:37:22.000 --> 00:37:22.880
If you are free,

00:37:23.800 --> 00:37:25.260
let's go get some skewers.

00:37:38.600 --> 00:37:39.240
Mr. Gu.

00:37:40.320 --> 00:37:41.720
How is the situation now?

00:37:41.880 --> 00:37:43.080
Let's talk on the way.

00:37:43.280 --> 00:37:43.800
Okay.

00:37:43.800 --> 00:37:44.520
Just now,

00:37:45.320 --> 00:37:46.760
the hospital called me.

00:38:19.800 --> 00:38:23.040
Xu Xu decided to overturn it.

00:38:23.040 --> 00:38:24.520
He must have his reasons.

00:38:24.520 --> 00:38:26.040
You should stop talking.

00:38:26.040 --> 00:38:27.700
You haven't had water all day.

00:38:27.720 --> 00:38:29.450
Talking will make you thirsty.

00:38:30.920 --> 00:38:32.080
Born to worry.

00:38:34.560 --> 00:38:35.240
I know.

00:38:36.760 --> 00:38:37.890
Don't worry so much.

00:38:38.400 --> 00:38:40.200
Your health comes first right now.

00:38:40.200 --> 00:38:42.060
We've got the best doctor for you.

00:38:43.640 --> 00:38:44.480
Several of us

00:38:44.800 --> 00:38:46.400
are waiting for you outside.

00:38:50.000 --> 00:38:52.440
You must not tell Wu Wei.

00:38:53.240 --> 00:38:54.300
Don't tell him yet.

00:38:54.640 --> 00:38:55.240
Okay.

00:40:15.200 --> 00:40:16.260
You knew all along.

00:40:16.560 --> 00:40:17.760
You knew everything.

00:40:18.560 --> 00:40:19.440
Let me explain.

00:40:20.760 --> 00:40:21.620
Don't touch me.

00:40:52.040 --> 00:40:52.600
Come.

00:40:56.760 --> 00:40:57.760
Sit down and wait.

00:42:12.120 --> 00:42:13.840
I don't have a mom anymore.

00:42:15.200 --> 00:42:16.880
I don't have a mom anymore.

00:42:22.400 --> 00:42:23.920
I don't have a mom anymore.

00:42:24.680 --> 00:42:26.400
I don't have a mom anymore.

